*> \endhtmlonly
*
*  Definition:
*  ===========
*
*       LOGICAL FUNCTION DISNAN( DIN )
*
*       .. Scalar Arguments ..
*       DOUBLE PRECISION, INTENT(IN) :: DIN
*       ..
*
*
*> \par Purpose:
*  =============
*>
*> \verbatim
*>
